  "privacy_title": "Privacy Policy",
  "privacy_body": "Voxna Privacy Policy\n\nLast updated: January 1, 2025\n\n1. Information We Collect\nVoxna collects the following information:\n- Voice recording data (stored only on your device)\n- Voice analysis metrics (energy, clarity, expression range, tempo)\n- Self-assessment data\n- App settings\n\n2. Data Storage\nAll data is stored in your device's local storage. Voice data and analysis results are never sent to external servers.\n\n3. Purpose of Data Use\nCollected data is used solely for visualizing voice changes and generating reports.\n\n4. Data Sharing\nWe do not share your data with third parties.\n\n5. Data Deletion\nAll data can be deleted through the \"Delete Account\" feature or by uninstalling the app.\n\n6. Contact\nFor questions about this policy, please use the in-app feedback feature.",

